  "unresolvedTextByHash": {
    "5400046ab1033c036dd50f9f2a196c9dff968d31b1f7fe2b8d22f28c655eea3a": "Ah, [?]. I'm sure you have plenty of questions. I will do my best to answer them.",
    "591fd1959181b979ed8ed072967ad0e497f1900f43d328847de083d85066ed77": "Ah [?]. I'm sure you have plenty of questions. I will do my best to answer them.",
    "2df9de1dd65203266c7f6a9aaad323000e51df52fadd08eb75b0e2b306dd237a": "Yes... You're right, [?]. I should not be so down. There is still a chance my kind can live on.",
    "38f6366c43ae4466ab10f1442b08e2ad50501e220b1deb8699ff9371226aef18": "I'm sorry, [?], but let us not speak of this further. To learn of the death of another of my kin is no surprise, but it pains me all the same. I would prefer to focus my thoughts elsewhere.",
    "d895f548a5e1e67f0a05a09d60eb34fa72e123e1d958d95d22c5d3f47cdc3912": "Ah, [?]. You made it.",
    "e40ebbe9b9139926855a1793dce14f0ff45a1d0b6aa3d4e63f315091493d5e91": "Thank you, [?]. That gives me some hope. If you have any more questions, do not hesitate to ask.",
    "a088bd6ef55a936ccf356569584e9f04fc17d832344f64394d40920bda67848e": "Thank you, [?]! You've given me hope that my kin can live on. If you need help with anything else, let me know.",
    "87738b7385394508a88ff3a6a1031f931a7640cef594edfce5313bb728e8d6ee": "I'll be here if you change your mind. Take care [?].",
    "d4f308b0836be1a97d04280a2489faaf7567a3144693101e1834de097936a62d": "I'm afraid there's not much I can do to help you [?]. My lack of vision means I can't work an anvil like I used to.",
    "13ae7085508da2bdf1504e634c23b7d801d8da01fab94af77e2e00997661a634": "You need a Barronite [?] and 1500 barronite shards.",
    "e8b40e651d1ff42154ab6694ce628acbef56f6096ba9d3e2bfbe295187922b98": "You're an brilliant cook [?]! Just don't bring me too many of these, I'm trying to watch my weight."
  }
}